-- Halkbank of Turkey Hires Eleven Banks For $500 Million One-Year Loan
-- Seda Sezer
-- 2010-06-29T15:01:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/halkbank-of-turkey-hires-eleven-banks-for-500-million-one-year-loan.html

          
          
             Turkiye Halk Bankasi AS, a Turkish
state-run lender hired 11 banks for a one-year syndicated loan
of a total $500 million in two tranches of dollars and euros,
according to a filing with the Istanbul Stock Exchange today.  
